text: Ede Szomjas (6 September 1914 - 8 March 1987) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:1987 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
